'''''Star Wars'' 13''' is the thirteenth issue in [[Dark Horse Comics|Dark Horse's]] [[Star Wars (2013)|''Star Wars'']] [[Star Wars comic books|comic book]] series. It was released on [[January 8]], [[2014]].

==Publisher's summary==
''After a defeat by Rebel forces and the escape of prisoner Luke Skywalker, Darth Vader decides to clean house. From one end of the galaxy to the other, Vader's "new broom"&mdash;a squad of elite stormtroopers backed by the Dark Lord's own lightsaber&mdash;is sweeping the ranks of the Empire!''

